arStrings.szText: Each cast of {c_important}Blood Lance{/c} will launch an additional {c_important}Blood Lance{/c} at a Nearby enemy when it first hits an enemy that is already lanced, dealing {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} of normal damage.
